name: War Serpent
description:
A tale about young boy who born as a snake.
A Snake with feathers and wings.
Each time The Young Snake swing his tail,
Rain and Storm follow.

All he had just his sister loves

One day The Young Snake rise from his cave.
Fly to the sky to challenge The Great Sun,
Only to plummet to the deepest sea

Since then,
In the middle of july.
Lands are trembling.
But The Young Snake Sisters heard a faint whisper.
" Dont worry, I will rise again "

By TukaTulu
